Wan’t to bring a guest (non-chalmerist) to the next Student Union pub crawl? We’re launching the all new Guest Pass – make sure you get one before the pub crawl. It must be purchased by a Chalmers Student and carried by the guest. Sold on campus from 13 th January 2014 at the following spots: J.A. Pripps, Kokboken (Lindholmen), Bibliotekscaféet and Café Bulten. The price is 10 SEK/pass. More on the Guest Pass, the Pub crawl and open pubs: [link](http://www.tinyurl.com/chspubrunda "link")[
